<item>
            <title>[HADOOP-10402] Configuration.getValByRegex does not substitute for variables</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-10402</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When using Configuration.getValByRegex(...), variables are not resolved.  &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For example:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-xml&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;property&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
   &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;name&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;bar&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/name&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
   &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;value&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;woot&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/value&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/property&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;property&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
   &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;name&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;foo3&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/name&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
   &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;value&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;${bar}&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/value&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/property&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you then try to do something like &lt;tt&gt;Configuration.getValByRegex(foo.*)&lt;/tt&gt;, it will return a Map containing &quot;foo3=${bar}&quot; instead of &quot;foo3=woot&quot;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
